  <lyrics>[V1]
 /K'anchaypiña kaspa, allinta qan puriy,
 Diosninchej rikumun./
 
[C]
 /Allinta qan puriy
 Diosninchej qhawamushasunki./
 
[V2]
 /Diosninchej qhawamun tukuy kay pachata,
 Allinta qan puriy./
 
[V3]
 /Señorllata qhaway, kasuy nisqasninta.
 Atípay sajrata./
 
</lyrics></song>